FBIS4-4779 "dreas065_d_94012" FBIS-EAS-94-065 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 South Korea Chongnyon Official on Kim Chong-il's Power Chongnyon Official on Kim Chong-il's Power SK0504102894 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network in Korean 0955 GMT 5 Apr 94 SK0504102894 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network Korean BFN [Text] Ho Chong-man, responsible vice chairman of Chongnyon [General Association of Korean Residents in Japan], today expressed his view that Kim Chong-il, secretary of the North Korean Workers Party, has completely been delegated full power--political, economic, and military--from his father Kim Il-song. Ho Chong-man said this at the Japan Socialist Party's Japan-Korean Committee general meeting held today at the First Lawmakers Hall of the Japanese Diet.
